      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car shows clear signs of age, including noticeable scratches and some minor dents on the exterior, as well as significant wear on the interior upholstery. It has been driven regularly and may require some upcoming maintenance to keep it in peak operating form. It\u2019s a dependable car that reflects its history of use, offered at a price that accounts for its current state.",
