    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior still carries a deep shine, though a close inspection will reveal some minor door dings and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that shows pride of ownership.",
