    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You've seriously gotta see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it stays spotless inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s in truly perfect shape and ready for a new home, this is the one! Shoot me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43900.0,
