    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality specimen. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, completely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks, thanks to a professional ceramic coating and climate-controlled garage storage. Inside, the cabin is impeccable; the leather remains supple with no creasing or bolster wear, and the factory-fresh scent persists. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service history and a spotless undercarriage that has never seen rain or salt. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle that will satisfy even the most meticulous collector. Inspections are highly encouraged to appreciate the level of care this car has received.",
      "price": 44500.0,
